        "section_value": "The patient reports throbbing pain in both sides of the knee, with more pain on the inside. He reports limping since the injury and that the pain has been getting worse. He has been taking Tylenol for the pain, but it's not completely effective and wears off after a couple of hours. He also reports pain in his left hand. The patient reports pain in the knee.",
